# Anthropic API key used server-side by the /api/chat serverless function.
# This key is NEVER exposed to the browser.
# Store this as a GitHub secret (ANTHROPIC_API_KEY) and configure it as an
# Azure Static Web Apps application setting in the deployment workflow.
#
# Local development:
#   Copy this file to .env.local and replace the placeholder with your real key.
#   Never commit .env.local to version control.
#
# Azure Static Web Apps deployment:
#   Store the key as a GitHub repository secret named ANTHROPIC_API_KEY.
#   Configure it as an application setting in the deploy workflow so the
#   serverless function can access it via process.env.ANTHROPIC_API_KEY.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
